        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The &amp;quot;Mukhyamantri Gram Parivahan Yojana&amp;quot; launched by the Transport Department, Government of Bihar, aimed at improving transportation facilities in all panchayats of the state. It offers financial assistance to beneficiaries for purchasing vehicles.\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n  - **Standard vehicles:** 50% of the purchase price or up to ₹1,00,000/-.  - **E-rickshaws:** 50% of the purchase price or up to ₹70,000/-.  - **Ambulances:** 50% of the purchase price or up to ₹2,00,000/-.\n",
        "exclusions_md": "<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The Scheme provides financial assistance for purchasing vehicles to enhance transportation facilities in rural areas. It includes grants for regular vehicles, e-rickshaws, and ambulances under specified conditions.",
