          "process_md": "**Registration Process:**\n**Step-1:** Visit the official [Website](https://state.bihar.gov.in/transport/SectionInformation.html?editForm&amp;amp;rowId=6353). Click on the &amp;amp;quot;Registration&amp;amp;quot; button.\n**Step-2:** Enter your Mobile Number, New Password, Email, and Driving License No. \n**Step-3:** Click on &amp;amp;quot;Register&amp;amp;quot; to complete the registration process.\n&amp;lt;br&amp;gt;\n\n**Application Process:**\n**Step-1:** Login with your registered Mobile Number and Password.\n**Step-2:** On the Application page, fill in all the required details and upload the relevant documents.\n**Step-3:** Then click on the declaration form and click on &amp;amp;quot;Submit&amp;amp;quot;.\n**Step-4:** Once all details are filled in correctly, click on &amp;amp;quot;Print Application&amp;amp;quot; to get a copy of the application form.\n"
